Carol Vorderman, 61, is known for her daily outfit snaps, and today was no different. The former Countdown star stunned as she took to her social media platforms to show off her "old hippy leggings". The bright orange skintight leggings showed off the presenter's killer curves, leaving very little to the imagination. Carol's trousers featured a flowing bottom, contributing to the "hippy" look. She captioned the post on Twitter in view of her 483,400 followers: "Back home ....my old hippy leggings on and off for a chinwag and being spoiled by my friends. "Happiest of days x."